=Description=

"Open Innovation tends to be a very conceptual practice. In this workshop we will instead give you 3 distinct tools that will help you guide you and your team through the three major steps in the innovation process: Inspiration, Ideation & Implementation. These tools will not only help you gain deeper insights into the main challenges you might face with every Open Innovation Initiative but also give you the understanding to tackle them. As you will see in the workshop, these tools will not only help you with Open Innovation but with an even wider variety of problems you might face on a daily basis."


